  <li><a href="https://smittenkitchen.com/">Smitten Kitchen</a>: Deb Perelman is what I imagine Nigella Lawson is to some people. She‚Äôs my go-to person for weeknight recipes and pastries. Most meal planning sessions start here.</li>
  <li><a href="https://alexandracooks.com/">Alexandra Cooks</a>: this website has excellent vegetarian recipes, another favorite for our meal planning.</li>
